==Vingod-vingod rupam==

Konknni bhaxechi vingod-vingod rupam pollounk melltat. Konknnicheo khubxeo boli bhaso asat. Tantutli ek mhonnge Malvani. Census Board of India ani ISO-n he bhaxek Konknnichi uloupachi bhas mhonn manyatai dilea.

==Sindhudurg, Dokxinn Ratnagiri==

[[Malvani]] bhas Konkanatle Sindhudurg, Dokxinn Ratnagiri (Lanja,Rajapur) che vatthara meren uloitat. Pan he bhaxecho mukhel vapor Sindhudurgat, mukhel korun Malvan,Vengurla,Kudal ani Sawantwadi (jaka Wadi mhan ulaytat) avathat jata.

