==Tech sabd==

'''Sakayl kaaym kaaym Malvani sabd dille asat je samake Konkanit ani Malvanit sarake asat:''' Khay, Thay, Jay, Maka,Tuka, Amaka, Tumaka, Vangad, Begin, Somato, Samako, raav, bhitar, bhayr,gajali,fakanda,Oogi, Chedu, Bayal, Gho etc. Kaaym kaaym aprachalit sabd je konkanit ani malvanit sarkech asat: nhay(nadi),yedul(hodal),sakayl,deg, vhad, nistyak.

Tashi vayar delli valeri khub vodali asa. He puray barpat ti dene shakya javache naa. Pun janka Konkaniche he bhasecho abhyas korinso dista tani hacher ayjun sansodhan korche.


